s in agreement with the observations. The\nsimulations reveal that the cooling flows cessed $\\sim 50 - 70$ Myr after the\nAGN jets are started.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 1 Feb 2011 18:50:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-02-02"}
